                <tr>
                  <td width="560" valign="top" bgcolor="#C4EECE" class="style2"><p class="style79"><strong><em>Its spring time, and everything's coming up consortia:</em></strong><em>&nbsp; There's a bumper crop of new organizations this month, covering a wide and diverse range of technical areas, constituencies and techniques – and an equally interesting diversity of strategic aims and game plans.</em></p></td>
